<#-- Arithmetic expressions -->
Price: $${price}
Quantity: ${quantity}
Subtotal: $${price * quantity}
Tax (8%): $${price * quantity * 0.08}
Total: $${price * quantity * 1.08}

<#-- Comparison expressions -->
Is expensive: ${price > 50}
Is bulk order: ${quantity >= 10}
Qualifies for discount: ${quantity >= 5 && price > 25}

<#-- Logical expressions -->
Premium user: ${user.isPremium}
Active subscription: ${user.hasSubscription}
Can access premium features: ${user.isPremium && user.hasSubscription}
Needs upgrade: ${!user.isPremium || !user.hasSubscription}

<#-- String concatenation (using +) -->
Full name: ${firstName + " " + lastName}
Welcome message: ${"Welcome, " + firstName + "!"}

<#-- Complex nested expressions -->
<#-- Note: Ternary operator not yet supported in VeeMarker -->
Simple calculation: $${price * quantity * 0.9}